      <title>垃圾债券赢得了从市场风暴中寻求平静的投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/junk-bonds-win-over-investors-seeking-calm-amid-market-storm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[垃圾键似乎不再那么垃圾了。近年来，美国的投资者正在堆积成一种资产类别，最近几周吸引了投资者寻求安全港免受市场动荡的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/junk-bonds-win-over-investors-seeking-calm-amid-market-storm</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 14:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
